Title: Sin City Blue
Plot: Two secretaries on holiday from Arizona attempt to steal a man's wallet and ATM pin number in a scam, and wind up dead in different locations. Meanwhile, the CSI team also investigates a disturbing medical mystery involving the dumping of human organs in a wildlife refuge.
Writer: David Rambo, Jacqueline Hoyt, Daniel Steck
GuestStars: James Frain, Raphael Sbarge, Sebastian Tillinger, Gene Farber, Jon Wellner, José Zúñiga, Bernardo Badillo, Rick Cramer, Jocelin Donahue, Rome Kanda, Emily Montague, Rachel Morihiro
